      <title>莱曼称他正在努力拯救美国 50 亿美元欺诈案</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-06/jorge-paulo-lemann-says-trying-to-save-americanas-after-5-billion-fraud</link>
